{"tid":757014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究：惡狗較短命","createTime":"2018-07-26T12:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T13:13:57.000Z","uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"56dafdd2b281d05d4203bb8f828996116a0030a1","tid":757014,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"英國研究：惡狗較短命<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】英國《動物福利》（Animal Welfare）昨刊出一項研究稱，過度吠叫、侵略及不服從的惡犬往往壽命不長。倫敦皇家獸醫學院的研究員參考了英國26.4萬隻狗的資料， 發現英國3歲以下的狗，有三分之一的死與品行不端或與之有關，當中有75%遭人道毁滅，其次是死於交通意外。研究人員稱，這突顯獸醫需接受進階行為教育，進一步協助寵物主人。狗的不良行為可能是有病的迹象，或因為欠訓練。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）"},{"pid":"91feef4b0d6c8dfe30154e9613923b096b7ea023","tid":757014,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"英國研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea37ce2ffe41dbb6bedad5ffe84aed813f66c2cf","tid":757014,"uid":35598,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"同隻狗講：<br />\n拿，你想長命啲，就乖乖地聽我話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d808cd688a5554a1ff3010a8516968cf696cfa","tid":757014,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:56:04.000Z","msg":"689呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43cd7e4d550e7c1c21f5d52406fdbbcf1509b40","tid":757014,"uid":60689,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"波台班手足一定好短命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c338300bbc5e2c8f0268118f64263bbd79cde0b","tid":757014,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"因為有人類干擾姐"},{"pid":"e8e7e772fb28ab5ccd1af50ca2b0f15d2ce60a5f","tid":757014,"uid":63588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"老納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e05f13b5e684e6248e4508b9013483d404ad5a5","tid":757014,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61d808cd688a5554a1ff3010a8516968cf696cfa","tid":757014,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T12:56:04.000Z","msg":"689呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"9都不如"},{"pid":"0f7b5bd43afb1c02d99f6b18899bba5a836f9da4","tid":757014,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:13:57.000Z","msg":"世界四大不可信：<br />\n<br />\n英國研究<br />\n中國製造<br />\n南韓起源<br />\n台灣報導"}]}